      • removeEdge

        public void removeEdge​(V from,
                       V to,
                       E label)
        Remove one edge from the graph
        Parameters:
        from - the outgoing vertex of the edge
        to - the edge to be removed
        label - the label of the edge to be removed
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if either from, to or label is null, or label is an empty string
        Modifies:
        this
        Effects:
        remove the edge label from the set of edges from vertex from to vertex to. If the set is empty, map vertex from to an empty HashMap.
        Requires:
        there exists an edge between from from to to
